{{Top|leg}}
A '''bo'tous''' was both the carrier and the creation of the [[bo'tous spore]]. Small insect-like creatures, they spawned from victims who had inhaled the spores and capable of tearing apart both the target, and if they were not careful, the host itself. Although short-lived, they grew extremely fast in the presence of [[Oxygen/Legends|oxygen]].

